<subject "Zavitan - a Web-based Seminars Management and Display System" />

<p>
Zavitan will be a web-based system for managing seminars (or lectures)
within an organization or another type of framework. The Technion hosts
several clubs, each giving lectures at irregular times, and there 
isn't a consistent, site-wide way to manage and display the lectures.
Zavitan aims to solve this, while still being suitable for other 
organizations who may need such functionality.
</p>

